(1, 'Privacy Policy', 'privacy-policy', '<h2>What is a Privacy Policy?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A Privacy Policy is a statement or a legal document that states how a company or website&nbsp;<strong>collects</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>handles</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>processes data</strong>&nbsp;of its customers and visitors. It explicitly describes whether that information is kept confidential, or is shared with or sold to third parties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Personal information about an individual may include the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Name</li>\r\n	<li>Address</li>\r\n	<li>Email</li>\r\n	<li>Phone number</li>\r\n	<li>Age</li>\r\n	<li>Sex</li>\r\n	<li>Marital status</li>\r\n	<li>Race</li>\r\n	<li>Nationality</li>\r\n	<li>Religious beliefs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>For example, an excerpt from&nbsp;<a href=\"https://policy.pinterest.com/en/privacy-policy\">Pinterest&#39;s</a>&nbsp;Privacy Policy agreement clearly describes the information Pinterest collects from its users as well as from any other source that users enable Pinterest to gather information from. The information that the user voluntarily gives includes names, photos, pins, likes, email address, and/or phone number etc., all of which is regarded as&nbsp;<strong>personal information</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Pinterest Privacy Policy: When you give it to us or give us permission to obtain it personal information clause\" src=\"https://www.privacypolicies.com/public/uploads/2018/06/pinterest-privacy-policy-collect-information-voluntarily-give-permission.jpg\" style=\"height:661px; width:630px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Additionally, Pinterest also states that it collects user location data from mobile&nbsp;</p>', '2022-08-30 12:58:16', '2022-08-30 12:58:16'),
(2, 'Return Policy', 'return-policy', '<h1>Returns and Exchanges</h1>\r\n\r\n<h2>The Airplane Shop Return/Refund Policy:</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Damaged Merchandise</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Should you receive a defective model, please contact our office at 1-800-752-6346, 973-244-1203 or&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@airplaneshop.com\">info@airplaneshop.com</a>, within 7 days for a return authorization. At that time a replacement will also be sent. You will be charged for replacement until the defective model is returned. Once the defective model is received we will issue a full refund which will be credited back to the original form of payment.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Standard Returns</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If for any reason you are not satisfied with your purchase, you must return it within 30 days for credit, exchange or refund. Models should be in their original packaging and condition. This does not require a return authorization, however please make sure you include paperwork in the box indicating your instructions. You must pay the shipping for your return/exchange. Once the package is returned we will issue a refund which will be credited back to the original form of payment. Refund will be for product only. Original shipping and return shipping not refundable. Please allow up to 10 business days to process your credit.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Please send all Returns for credit or exchange to:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The Airplane Shop<br />\r\n24 Stewart Place<br />\r\nUnit 4<br />\r\nFairfield, NJ 07004-163</p>', '2022-08-30 13:00:17', '2022-08-30 13:00:17');
